title: How-To: Make Shrimp Parm on Steroids with Meyhem Lauren
description:
Meyhem Lauren is back in the MUNCHIES Test Kitchen with another mind blowing recipe: shrimp parm on steroids. Dressed for the occasion and armed with a single fork, Meyhem upgrades this shrimp parm by adding lots of black pepper, cayenne pepper, and red pepper flakes. This is your shrimp parm on steroids.

Check out the recipe here: https://munchies.vice.com/en_us/article/pg5mv8/shrimp-parmesan
